overview: The four students Steve, Chris, Kathrin & Dennis are traumatized. Since their professor got murdered, a whole killing spree has started in town. And so the students were drawn into a hellhole full of hallucinations, drug abuse and violence. SIKKFUKKS is the first experimental/trash/splatter/horror movie by Nut-Wombat Studios starring Kockman, Ocelot-767, Chriso, Pascal, [S]Kill, Kathrin, Jakky & Cash
title: Sikkfukks
